race.comment: REBORN GYPSY (4) filled the minor money two on end before breaking through for a deserved win last time, scoring at Richmond over 401m (22.39). Comes through a solid form race last start. Hard to go past. BATGIRL (1) steps out for the first time at this track. In the money last start when second (25.27) at Goulburn over 440m. Leading chance. FANCY BELLA (5) got the job done again to make it two on end at Nowra over 365m (20.78). Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. In great form and can continue her winning ways. ESME WATSON (2) will be hard to beat with a drop in distance.
